    <briefdescription>
<para>Parameters for sending a periodic advertising response. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct contains the parameters used when sending a response to a periodic advertising request (see <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1gaae6b8583f7d5457f20b03dccd146425e" kindref="member">bt_le_per_adv_set_response_data</ref> function). The response is sent in the specified subevent and response slot, and includes event and subevent counters to track the request the response corresponds to. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
